<HEADLINE> Mountain Landslide In China Kills Two Farmers </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
LANZHOU, March 17 (Xinhua)-- Two people died in a recent
landslide on a mountainside in northwestern China's Gansu Province.
</P>
<P>
