<HEADLINE> Chinese Basketball League Results </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, March 17 (Xinhua) -- Following are the 21st round
results of the Chinese Basketball League on Wednesday (host teams
in CAPS):
</P>
<P>
BAYI ROCKETS bt Shandong Flaming Bulls 107-105 (49-55 halftime)
