<TEXT>
<P>
YANGON, March 17 (Xinhua) -- Myanmar opened its embassy in
Phnom Penh, Cambodia, on Tuesday to further strengthen the
friendly and cooperative relations between the two countries, a
press release from the Myanmar Foreign Ministry said Wednesday.
</P>
<P>
