felling.
</P>
<P>
Precautionary measures are also being taken to avert
possibilities of wildfire and protect forest against diseases and
pest attack.
</P>
<P>
Ethiopia's forested area, which was 40 percent of the land
mass 50 years ago, has been reduced to a mere 2.5 percent in
recent years.  
