Luis Jalandoni has confirmed that Bishop Roman Tiples, general
secretary of the National Council of Churches in the Philippines,
and Bishop Alberto Ramento of the Philippine Independent Church
will go to Utrecht in the Netherlands "in a few days."
</P>
