In Davao del Norte, troops sent to rescue Obillo and Montealto
encountered 20 NPA rebels Monday about 9 a.m.
</P>
<P>
The two Protestant bishops leaving for Utrecht are in addition
to the four Catholic clergymen and a former government peace
negotiator already in the Netherlands to negotiate with the NDF
for the release of Obillo, Montealto, Police Chief Insp. Roberto
Bernal and Sgt. Alipio Lozada.
