<HEADLINE> Macedonians Protest NATO Deployment in Kosovo </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
TIRANA, March 16 (Xinhua) -- About 3,000 Serb Macedonians held
a rally in the capital city of Skopje on Tuesday, protesting
against the stationing of NATO troops in their country and the
planned deployment in Kosovo.
</P>
<P>
According to the Macedonian Informative Agency (MIA), the
protesters, chanting slogans against NATO and the United States,
urged the Macedonian government to close the border to prevent the
