somewhere in Britain if we can match the same sort of money that
is put up by the Americans.
</P>
<P>
"We hope that maybe Tony Banks will intervene and get the
private sector involved. He has talked about bringing the big
sporting events to this country. We can sit down and talk and
find a way to do this," he added. 
